    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 1,
    "last_activity_date" : 1409578850,
    "creation_date" : 1409578850,
    "answer_id" : 25607143,
    "question_id" : 225337,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>you can split a string by line break by using the following statement :</p>\n\n<pre><code> String textStr[] = yourString.split(\"\\\\r?\\\\n\");\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>you can split a string by Whitespace by using the following statement :</p>\n\n<pre><code>String textStr[] = yourString.split(\"\\\\s+\");\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
